{"tid":549371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"39歲休班女輔警打傷12歲女童被捕","createTime":"2018-02-03T14:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T12:51:06.000Z","uid":5195,"like":206,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"b347e8a46513f26e1e0e7f61dd000391b9d8e631","tid":549371,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:11:52.000Z","msg":"休班女輔警涉襲擊女童被捕。上月28日中午12許，一名姓盧(39歲)休班女輔警，在葵涌興盛路93號葵涌運動場內，因瑣事襲擊一名12歲女童。警方接報到場，經初步調查，以涉嫌襲擊致造成實際身體傷害拘捕盧。女童報稱肩部受傷，盧亦稱腰痛，同被送至瑪嘉烈醫院治理。盧已獲准保釋候查，須於2月下旬向警方報到，案件交葵青警區重案組跟進。<br />\n<br />\n警隊表示，非常重視警員的操守，任何人員干犯違法行為，警隊絕不容忍和姑息，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。"},{"pid":"be643d785d186ec9bcdb65afe4432441f2a98c89","tid":549371,"uid":63950,"like":102,"dislike":0,"score":102,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:22:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4cdf682baac2630be8f27f21c479422cef028b8a","tid":549371,"uid":63950,"like":53,"dislike":3,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:22:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c98490ce46720319c337c982578412337a062bc5","tid":549371,"uid":37413,"like":115,"dislike":1,"score":114,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:24:45.000Z","msg":"全港最大犯罪集團上線啦！"},{"pid":"1712cd5bb0a5100809e32589334aa398e6b5b24c","tid":549371,"uid":126529,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:24:52.000Z","msg":"39對12 <br />\n知唔知醜"},{"pid":"e4cdf53bf8da515d591230a813f6d01a71bc5be0","tid":549371,"uid":123591,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:25:08.000Z","msg":"警犬最愛打人同偷野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d18eb4d55153bc8190beef7a0053ac8e04ee9c1d","tid":549371,"uid":79137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:25:11.000Z","msg":"慈母巧偉大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347a9e0b82f7c75be47e21ad66e6d25d8c6daba4","tid":549371,"uid":48334,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T14:26:12.000Z","msg":"Madam 教女唔洗你教"},{"pid":"5167655775f